➜半场两次违体，京粤G2火药味十足！林书豪与尤度25+12对轰威姆斯
http://www.sohu.com/a/411835142_343291	47276
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200806/c8a0a265ef1f4b859349b9151e5c807c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
